<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11484&amp;p=131914#p131914"><![CDATA[
Did it really say just &quot;MMC&quot;, or did it say MMC1 or MMC3? In the case of MMC1, the biggest difference is a corner case related to battery save. In the case of MMC3, the difference is whether or not scanline IRQs can fire on consecutive scanlines.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sat Aug 02, 2014 6:30 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
